summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending plat 219W, page 3, of the official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300), to rezone Lots 1 and 2, Block 4, Allendale Addition from RS 7200 to RM 800 contingent upon the execution of a Property Use and Development Agreement (Petition of Woodland Enterprises, C.F. 283316).
